Supra Mahumapelo must fall on his assegai like his patron Jacob  Zuma and  others who have disgraced themselves and the  ANC. Look at Hlaudi Motsoeneng, Richard Mdluli, Dudu Myeni, Ellen Tshabalala and Kgomotso Phahlane. Next are Tom Moyane, Arthur Fraser and the  Guptas. But we must never use vulgar politics, the destruction of property, the stoning of cars and the  looting of shops to get rid of him and others. We must be revolutionary. Siyanda Mhlongo KwaDukuza